Parties and events took place throughout the Commonwealth. In 2002, Elizabeth marked her Golden Jubilee, the 50th anniversary of her accession. Elizabeth's 2012 Diamond Jubilee marked 60 years on the throne, and celebrations were held throughout her realms, the wider Commonwealth, and beyond.
